莉薩·安在[[Eminem|Eminem]]的音樂視頻《{{Link-en|我們製造你|We Made You}}》中再次扮演莎拉·佩林<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://business.avn.com/articles/34816.html|title=Lisa Ann appears in new Eminem video|accessdate=April 3, 2009|archive-date=2009-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090327060520/http://business.avn.com/articles/34816.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，她得以演出實在有賴導演{{Link-en|約瑟夫·卡恩|Joseph Kahn}}的建議<ref name=XRent/>。

